South Africa Names 2 Non-Executive Board Members to Reserve Bank

-- B y   A n d r e s   R .   M a r t i n e z
-- 
2011-10-14T12:29:09Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-14/south-africa-names-2-non-executive-board-members-to-reserve-bank.html
South African President  Jacob Zuma 
appointed two non-executive directors to the board of the
nation’s  Reserve Bank .  Maureen Makole Manyama-Matome and Tania Ajam were named to
the board, according to a statement posted on the presidency’s
website.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Andres R. Martinez at 
 amartinez28@bloomberg.net  